================================================================================
GENERATED AND EXTERNAL GAMES — DEFAULT LICENSE BOUNDARY
================================================================================

The `games/` directory is a local output and integration area. Game projects
placed here are consumers of Studio Foundation; they are not automatically part
of the Foundation distribution.

Each game must declare its own license. Unless a game directory includes a
LICENSE file that grants additional rights, its content is all rights reserved
by its respective copyright holders.

Studio Foundation code under `engine/`, `services/`, `tools/`, `shared/`,
`templates/`, `docs/`, `infra/`, `scripts/`, and `tests/` remains
licensed under the repository root LICENSE.
